---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import HeroBanner from '../components/HeroBanner.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Full Truck Load" description="Full Truck Load shipping services - entire semi-trailer container shipping across 48 states.">
  
  <HeroBanner title="Full Truck Load" backgroundImage="/images/hero-truck.png" />

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-section">
        <div class="content-section__text">
          <h2>Full Truck Load Services</h2>
          <p>We can ship an entire semi-trailer container for you for any states in the US except Alaska and Hawaii, and it is the same for Less-Than Truckload.</p>
          <p>Lane Logistics Group has built a vast broker network that is dedicated to serving shippers in 48 states. Our team of logistics professionals is committed to ensuring that your freight is transported safely and efficiently.</p>
          <p>We understand the importance of timely delivery and work diligently to ensure that your cargo arrives at its destination on schedule. Our extensive network of trusted carriers allows us to provide reliable and cost-effective full truck load shipping solutions.</p>
          <p>Whether you need to ship large quantities of goods across state lines or require specialized handling for your cargo, our full truck load services are designed to meet your needs.</p>
          <a href="/contact-us" class="btn btn--primary" style="margin-top:15px;">Request A Quote</a>
        </div>
        <div class="content-section__image">
          <img src="/images/ftl-truck.png" alt="Full Truck Load" loading="lazy" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>
